{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "守城之法，木為蒼旗，火為赤旗，薪樵為黃旗，石為白旗，水為黑旗，食為菌旗，死士為倉英之旗，竟士為雩旗，多卒為雙兔之旗，五尺童子為童旗，女子為梯末之旗，弩為狗旗，戟為旌旗，劍盾為羽旗，車為龍旗，騎為鳥旗。", "text_normalized": "守城之法，木為蒼旗，火為赤旗，薪樵為黃旗，石為白旗，水為黑旗，食為菌旗，死士為倉英之旗，竟士為雩旗，多卒為雙兔之旗，五尺童子為童旗，女子為梯末之旗，弩為狗旗，戟為旌旗，劍盾為羽旗，車為龍旗，騎為鳥旗。", "canonical_ref": "50.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "凡所求索旗名不在書者，皆以其形名為旗。", "text_normalized": "凡所求索旗名不在書者，皆以其形名為旗。", "canonical_ref": "50.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "城上舉旗，備具之官致財物，之足而下旗。", "text_normalized": "城上舉旗，備具之官致財物，之足而下旗。", "canonical_ref": "50.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "凡守城之法：", "text_normalized": "凡守城之法：", "canonical_ref": "50.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "石有積，樵薪有積，菅茅有積，雚葦有積，木有積，炭有積，沙有積，松柏有積，蓬艾有積，麻脂有積，金鐵有積，粟米有積；", "text_normalized": "石有積，樵薪有積，菅茅有積，雚葦有積，木有積，炭有積，沙有積，松柏有積，蓬艾有積，麻脂有積，金鐵有積，粟米有積；", "canonical_ref": "50.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "井灶有處，重質有居，五兵各有旗，節各有辨；", "text_normalized": "井灶有處，重質有居，五兵各有旗，節各有辨；", "canonical_ref": "50.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "法令各有貞；", "text_normalized": "法令各有貞；", "canonical_ref": "50.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "輕重分數各有請：", "text_normalized": "輕重分數各有請：", "canonical_ref": "50.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "主慎道路者有經。", "text_normalized": "主慎道路者有經。", "canonical_ref": "50.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "亭尉各為幟，竿長二丈五，帛長丈五，廣半幅者大。", "text_normalized": "亭尉各為幟，竿長二丈五，帛長丈五，廣半幅者大。", "canonical_ref": "50.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "寇傅攻前池外廉，城上當隊鼓三，舉一幟；", "text_normalized": "寇傅攻前池外廉，城上當隊鼓三，舉一幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "到水中周，鼓四，舉二幟；", "text_normalized": "到水中周，鼓四，舉二幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "到藩，鼓五，舉三幟；", "text_normalized": "到藩，鼓五，舉三幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "到馮垣，鼓六，舉四幟；", "text_normalized": "到馮垣，鼓六，舉四幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "到女垣，鼓七，舉五幟；", "text_normalized": "到女垣，鼓七，舉五幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "到大城，鼓八，舉六幟；", "text_normalized": "到大城，鼓八，舉六幟；", "canonical_ref": "50.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "乘大城半以上，鼓無休。", "text_normalized": "乘大城半以上，鼓無休。", "canonical_ref": "50.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "夜以火，如此數。", "text_normalized": "夜以火，如此數。", "canonical_ref": "50.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "寇卻解，輒部幟如進數，而無鼓。", "text_normalized": "寇卻解，輒部幟如進數，而無鼓。", "canonical_ref": "50.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "城為隆，長五十尺，四面四門將長四十尺，其次三十尺，其次二十五尺，其次二十尺，其次十五尺，高無下四十五尺。", "text_normalized": "城為隆，長五十尺，四面四門將長四十尺，其次三十尺，其次二十五尺，其次二十尺，其次十五尺，高無下四十五尺。", "canonical_ref": "50.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "城上吏卒置之背，卒於頭上，城下吏卒置之肩。", "text_normalized": "城上吏卒置之背，卒於頭上，城下吏卒置之肩。", "canonical_ref": "50.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "左軍於左肩，中軍置之胸。", "text_normalized": "左軍於左肩，中軍置之胸。", "canonical_ref": "50.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "各一鼓，中軍一三。", "text_normalized": "各一鼓，中軍一三。", "canonical_ref": "50.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "每鼓三、十擊之，諸有鼓之吏，謹以次應之，當應鼓而不應，不當應而應鼓，主者斬。", "text_normalized": "每鼓三、十擊之，諸有鼓之吏，謹以次應之，當應鼓而不應，不當應而應鼓，主者斬。", "canonical_ref": "50.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "道廣三十步，於城下夾階者，各二，其井置鐵甕。", "text_normalized": "道廣三十步，於城下夾階者，各二，其井置鐵甕。", "canonical_ref": "50.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "於道之外為屏，三十步而為之圜，高丈。", "text_normalized": "於道之外為屏，三十步而為之圜，高丈。", "canonical_ref": "50.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "為民圂，垣高十二尺以上。", "text_normalized": "為民圂，垣高十二尺以上。", "canonical_ref": "50.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "巷術周道者，必為之門，門二人守之，非有信符，勿行，不從令者斬。", "text_normalized": "巷術周道者，必為之門，門二人守之，非有信符，勿行，不從令者斬。", "canonical_ref": "50.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "城中吏卒民男女，皆辨異衣章微職，令男女可知。", "text_normalized": "城中吏卒民男女，皆辨異衣章微職，令男女可知。", "canonical_ref": "50.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "諸守牲格者，三出卻適，守以令召賜食前，予大旗，署百戶邑若他人財物，建旗其署，令皆明白知之，曰某子旗。", "text_normalized": "諸守牲格者，三出卻適，守以令召賜食前，予大旗，署百戶邑若他人財物，建旗其署，令皆明白知之，曰某子旗。", "canonical_ref": "50.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "牲格內廣二十五步，外廣十步，表以地形為度。", "text_normalized": "牲格內廣二十五步，外廣十步，表以地形為度。", "canonical_ref": "50.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants", "source_id": "mozi-050-flags-and-pennants__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "勒卒，中教解前後左右，卒勞者更休之。", "text_normalized": "勒卒，中教解前後左右，卒勞者更休之。", "canonical_ref": "50.32", "notes": ""}
